{"tid":2178043,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"出讓台灣貓糧 想試又唔知啱唔啱食既入來","createTime":"2020-08-28T06:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T04:16:58.000Z","uid":94363,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"34ddc4ad7a4494256241e4fdc350cb1d963a63eb","tid":2178043,"uid":94363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"隻貓腸胃敏感 每種糧/罐食幾日就會軟/痾 所以之前買咗好多罐/糧俾佢試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家轉食全生肉好穩定 所以出讓返剩低既台系汪喵同怪獸部落罐頭同糧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sezkG8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsezkG8B.jpg&h=efd38861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怪獸部落兩種肉主食罐(82g)有<br />\r\n鵝雞肉*6 雞鯖魚*5 鰹鮭魚*4 鱉(水魚)雞肉*3 羊雞肉*3<br />\r\n官網原價48台幣(13HKD)每罐 現售每罐10HKD 須至少買5罐<br />\r\n細罐全部要晒送6罐怪獸部落湯罐(價值約30hkd)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iydtQ19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiydtQ19.jpg&h=dae5b56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n汪喵星球主食罐（165g)有<br />\r\n火雞*4 牛雞肉*4 鰹魚蝦仁雞肉*4 鴨雞肉*4 鵪鶉雞肉*2 羊雞肉*2 鱈魚雞肉*3<br />\r\n官網原價每罐72台幣(19港幣) 現售每罐15港幣 <br />\r\n要晒大罐送毛起來虱目魚鬆 或 芝士雞肉鬆 原價70hkd<br />\r\n<br />\r\n以上罐頭全部要晒再9折 送多4罐汪喵肉蓉罐（約值85hkd)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cSN6DO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cSN6DO.png&h=9558a119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怪獸部落原肉慢烘乾糧 800g &lt;同類產品最平 成份最靚 可參考隔籬貓糧成份post<br />\n計返原價980台幣(250HKD) 買一送一 送嗰包係開過 一買返來隻衰貓咬穿咗本身個袋 所以即刻轉以密實袋裝住 只係試餵咗10g佢唔食就無再試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cn6GrDV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCn6GrDV.png&h=0702da65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪喵凍乾500g裝<br />\n雞*2 牛雞*1 原價980台幣/1280台幣<br />\n售250hkd雞 320牛雞<br />\n全部要晒可以再9折/ 計返880但送個日本タニタ既3kg 精密至0.1g食物磅（原價2850羊 200hkd)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%82%BF%E3%83%8B%E3%82%BF-%E3%82%B9%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB-0-1g-%E3%83%87%E3%82%B8%E3%82%BF%E3%83%AB-KD-320/dp/B002P67LH2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2F%25E3%2582%25BF%25E3%2583%258B%25E3%2582%25BF-%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2582%25B1%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25AB-0-1g-%25E3%2583%2587%25E3%2582%25B8%25E3%2582%25BF%25E3%2583%25AB-KD-320%2Fdp%2FB002P67LH2&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=182514b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%82%BF%E3%83%8B%E3%82%BF-%E3%82%B9%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB-0-1g-%E3%83%87%E3%82%B8%E3%82%BF%E3%83%AB-KD-320/dp/B002P67LH2</a>"},{"pid":"15fdd7f24afed40d4cd49d5f6438abcccaf7a507","tid":2178043,"uid":94363,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:30:30.000Z","msg":"罐頭歡迎只買少量（5罐起）買少又無得免運費 買多又唔知啱唔啱 可以買少少試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntg @MasterTheGreatKungYeung"},{"pid":"5526bc426f9b9a67ba9b4398bef9b1c8a78076c4","tid":2178043,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"邊到交收?"},{"pid":"4938f8bc139e7069fcc5dc75b487da09ecbd6b20","tid":2178043,"uid":94363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5526bc426f9b9a67ba9b4398bef9b1c8a78076c4","tid":2178043,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"邊到交收?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"我差唔多全日都喺ssp附近"},{"pid":"905ac83fec8c1a806f61ba67a314bbecbe08d31f","tid":2178043,"uid":6031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"要哂全部罐有得免運?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ca3aeafe47bda57751ca4db99b9551e2f14467","tid":2178043,"uid":94363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"暫時被巴絲hold晒了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a5bafe2c90f01f38d741f74544e1504f6cdad7","tid":2178043,"uid":201581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:36:02.000Z","msg":"想問全生肉餐係點？